# Path Alias Imports

Always use path aliases when importing local modules (e.g., `@prisma/*` → `src/prisma/*`).

If path aliases are not configured, set them up in `tsconfig` before adding new local imports.

Example:

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import { PrismaService } from '@prisma/prisma.service';

// ❌ BAD
import { PrismaService } from '../../prisma/prisma.service';
```
